snippet.title: How to host a Bingo on your Twitch channel - Live Bingo tutorial
snippet.description:
Host a live game of Bingo on your Twitch channel!

Install Live Bingo:
http://bit.ly/3b7io6p

If you need support or have any questions join our Discord:
https://discord.gg/U9DdwM6

0:00 How to install Live Bingo
0:25 Extension Permissions
1:14 Overlay vs Component
2:00 Bingo scoreboard on OBS
3:48 Create a game of Bingo
6:28 Draw numbers in your Bingo
8:28 What happens when a viewer calls Bingo
9:25 Ending
9:56 How your viewers will see Live Bingo on your channel
